<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 06:11:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军将哈马斯恐怖分子送回军事基地，据称以色列士兵在那里虐待他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-sends-hamas-terrorist-back-to-army-base-where-israeli-soldiers-allegedly-abused-him/00000191-0b08-de2c-a7ff-4f29ca4e0000</link><description>这名被拘留者已被转移到斯德泰曼的野战医院，涉嫌虐待他的士兵的同事仍在医院服役，其中一些人参加了要求释放的示威活动。以色列国防军表示，出于安全原因，不会透露被拘留者的位置信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:05:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-sends-hamas-terrorist-back-to-army-base-where-israeli-soldiers-allegedly-abused-him/00000191-0b08-de2c-a7ff-4f29ca4e0000</guid></item><item><title>一场暗杀的余兴节目，而不是以色列与哈马斯的人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/an-assassination-sideshow-instead-of-an-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/00000191-0a75-d4cf-afb5-4ef5ab250000</link><description>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚周三在德黑兰被杀后的一个大问题是，他的死将如何影响以色列和哈马斯之间的人质谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/an-assassination-sideshow-instead-of-an-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/00000191-0a75-d4cf-afb5-4ef5ab250000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心数月战争，美国和法国加大力度阻止以色列与伊朗和真主党对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/western-mediators-fear-latest-assassinations-raise-risk-of-israel-war-with-hezbollah-iran/00000191-0adf-d4cf-afb5-4edf47740000</link><description>美国不理会以色列军队与真主党发生“短暂但激烈”冲突的说法，尤其担心长期战争，因为白宫官员认为这会损害哈里斯获胜的机会</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/western-mediators-fear-latest-assassinations-raise-risk-of-israel-war-with-hezbollah-iran/00000191-0adf-d4cf-afb5-4edf47740000</guid></item><item><title>自 10 月 7 日以来，内塔尼亚胡从未如此受欢迎。他计划充分利用这一优势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hasnt-been-this-popular-since-october-7-he-plans-on-taking-full-advantage/00000191-0af0-dc54-a7dd-fff23bd20000</link><description>周三晚上，以色列总理站在人民面前，承担了责任 — — 但仅限于贝鲁特暗杀 — — 因为毕竟，成功只有一个父亲 ■ 几乎所有以色列人对暗杀事件感到满意是可以理解的；因为，几乎所有以色列人对暗杀事件感到满意是可以理解的。问题是内塔尼亚胡现在是否会停止破坏人质交易，还是继续受到极右翼的勒索</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:02:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hasnt-been-this-popular-since-october-7-he-plans-on-taking-full-advantage/00000191-0af0-dc54-a7dd-fff23bd20000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯和真主党领导人被杀后，以色列必须做好全面战火的准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-be-ready-for-all-out-conflagration-after-killing-of-hamas-hezbollah-leaders/00000191-0a35-d833-ab9f-cb37c3a40000</link><description>以色列显然已经准备好冒险，以打破与伊朗及其代理人的消耗循环。问题是，火势的高度很难控制，尤其是当火势有升级的趋势时。事实上，伊朗现在也处于寻求报复的境地，这将使平静变得更加难以实现</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-be-ready-for-all-out-conflagration-after-killing-of-hamas-hezbollah-leaders/00000191-0a35-d833-ab9f-cb37c3a40000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心全面战争迫在眉睫，人质家人在以色列各地开始了一天的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-live/irans-leader-reportedly-orders-direct-attack-on-israel-in-response-to-haniyehs-killing/00000191-0b96-dc1a-a1b7-1bfe53f00000</link><description>据报道，伊朗最高领袖下令对以色列进行直接攻击，以回应哈尼亚被杀事件。 ■ 联合国安理会成员国对全面中东战争的风险表示警惕。因安全局势而向北转移 ■ 由于以色列与真主党关系紧张，澳大利亚敦促公民离开黎巴嫩 ■ 伊朗联合国代表团：对哈尼亚遇刺事件的回应将令人遗憾 ■ 以色列在约旦河西岸发生刺伤袭击后伤势严重</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 01:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-live/irans-leader-reportedly-orders-direct-attack-on-israel-in-response-to-haniyehs-killing/00000191-0b96-dc1a-a1b7-1bfe53f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院：即使在战争期间，以色列国防军也必须保护巴勒斯坦人免受约旦河西岸定居者的侵害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-idf-must-protect-palestinians-from-west-bank-settlers-even-during-war/00000191-0a36-dc1a-a1b7-1bfea11d0000</link><description>高等法院针对西岸巴勒斯坦居民提出的请愿作出裁决，他们声称他们没有得到来自暴力犹太定居者的安全保护</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-idf-must-protect-palestinians-from-west-bank-settlers-even-during-war/00000191-0a36-dc1a-a1b7-1bfea11d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备应对伊朗对定点清除的多线反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-irans-multi-front-response-to-targeted-killings/00000191-09c1-d833-ab9f-cbe39eaa0000</link><description>随着以色列国防军增加在约旦河西岸的部署，以色列最高级国防官员对真主党和伊朗的预期反应感到左右为难。与此同时，以色列北部社区处于高度戒备状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-irans-multi-front-response-to-targeted-killings/00000191-09c1-d833-ab9f-cbe39eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>神圣化死亡：以色列人为何庆祝暗杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/sanctifying-death-why-israelis-celebrate-assassinations/00000191-0976-daf5-a7db-eff6a53b0000</link><description>“犹太力量”是极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔领导的奥兹玛·耶胡迪特党的直译，它正在影响这场战争。以色列已成为纵火狂的俄罗斯套娃</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/sanctifying-death-why-israelis-celebrate-assassinations/00000191-0976-daf5-a7db-eff6a53b0000</guid></item><item><title>达美航空、联合航空和英国航空取消飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/delta-united-and-british-airways-cancel-flights-to-israel/00000191-0a03-dc54-a7dd-ffc332690000</link><description>由于地区紧张局势，两家美国航空公司取消了部分航班 ■ 英国航空周四的航班也取消</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:46:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/delta-united-and-british-airways-cancel-flights-to-israel/00000191-0a03-dc54-a7dd-ffc332690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 299 天：英国部长在卡塔尔推动以色列与哈马斯休战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-299-u-k-ministers-in-qatar-to-push-for-israel-hamas-truce/00000191-098f-d4cf-afb5-4ddf6e1e0000</link><description>哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼耶 (Ismail Hanieh) 在德黑兰发动导弹袭击，以色列尚未宣称对此事负责 ■ 伊朗最高领袖：为哈尼耶遇刺报仇是“德黑兰的责任” ■ 以色列关闭哈德拉 (Hadera) 以北领空 24 小时 ■ 法院延长对涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者 ■ 战争进入 299 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-299-u-k-ministers-in-qatar-to-push-for-israel-hamas-truce/00000191-098f-d4cf-afb5-4ddf6e1e0000</guid></item><item><title>一个危险的谬论：特朗普再次担任总统对以色列不利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-dangerous-fallacy-another-trump-presidency-would-not-be-good-for-israel/00000191-087b-d3e8-adbd-b8ffca810000</link><description>上周，内塔尼亚胡总理拜访了1月6日叛乱的煽动者。本周，以色列发生了极右翼骚乱。那么，太多希望特朗普连任白宫的以色列人的妄想背后隐藏着什么呢？</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-dangerous-fallacy-another-trump-presidency-would-not-be-good-for-israel/00000191-087b-d3e8-adbd-b8ffca810000</guid></item><item><title>哈尼亚之死对哈马斯来说是一个打击，但历史证明总会有替代者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-death-is-a-blow-to-hamas-but-history-proves-theres-always-a-replacement/00000191-089e-dd42-af99-edff95120000</link><description>哈尼亚的遇刺是对哈马斯领导层的威胁，也是对伊朗和真主党的挑衅。尽管如此，这并不是一场“组织地震”，哈马斯政治局的其他几名成员可以轻松取代他</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:56:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-death-is-a-blow-to-hamas-but-history-proves-theres-always-a-replacement/00000191-089e-dd42-af99-edff95120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的暗杀政策只会让哈马斯、真主党和伊朗更加坚定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-assassination-policy-only-makes-hamas-hezbollah-and-iran-more-determined/00000191-08b7-d3e8-adbd-b8f7eced0000</link><description>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和福阿德·舒克在德黑兰和贝鲁特的暗杀事件展示了以色列的能力，但定点清除的学说本身已成为目的，而不是实现实际战略目标的一种方式</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israels-assassination-policy-only-makes-hamas-hezbollah-and-iran-more-determined/00000191-08b7-d3e8-adbd-b8f7eced0000</guid></item><item><title>别跟我谈论战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/dont-talk-to-me-about-the-war/00000191-08fe-d61c-a5bb-fefeeb780000</link><description>以色列市场和消费者似乎没有意识到以色列在本周发生两起暗杀事件后面临的风险。否认主义一直是加沙战争的主题</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/dont-talk-to-me-about-the-war/00000191-08fe-d61c-a5bb-fefeeb780000</guid></item><item><title>哈尼亚在伊朗首都被杀后，电视节目“德黑兰”的以色列明星分享了含糊其辞的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-star-of-tv-show-tehran-shares-coy-message-after-haniyeh-killed-in-iran/00000191-08cb-dd56-a9f5-69cbaf2b0000</link><description>出生于耶路撒冷的女演员尼夫·苏丹 (Niv Sultan) 在 Apple TV 间谍惊悚片中饰演摩萨德特工，她在社交媒体帖子中对着镜头眨眼，巧妙地暗示她的角色参与其中。以色列尚未确认对哈尼亚遇刺事件负责</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 13:29:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-star-of-tv-show-tehran-shares-coy-message-after-haniyeh-killed-in-iran/00000191-08cb-dd56-a9f5-69cbaf2b0000</guid></item><item><title>“为什么现在杀他”：以色列人质家庭担心哈尼亚被杀对停火协议的影响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-killing-raises-concern-among-hostages-families-over-impact-to-cease-fire-deal/00000191-0735-dd56-a9f5-6f77efef0000</link><description>“为什么现在既然已经达成协议，他们却选择杀了他？”一名人质的亲戚问道。虽然哈尼亚之死的影响很难预测，但它可能会软化以色列现在已经取得“胜利形象”的立场</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-killing-raises-concern-among-hostages-families-over-impact-to-cease-fire-deal/00000191-0735-dd56-a9f5-6f77efef0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室拒绝透露参加锡安之翼飞往美国航班的乘客名单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-refuses-to-disclose-list-of-passengers-on-wing-of-zion-flight-to-u-s/00000191-0863-d3e8-adbd-b8f756f80000</link><description>据报道，总理的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡本周返回以色列，该办公室还拒绝回答他是否登上了从华盛顿返回的航班。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 12:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-refuses-to-disclose-list-of-passengers-on-wing-of-zion-flight-to-u-s/00000191-0863-d3e8-adbd-b8f756f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党之间的“反应方程”已达到极限，但尚未被撕裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/the-response-equation-between-israel-and-hezbollah-is-stretched-to-its-limits/00000191-0859-dc27-abdb-fe79d0bb0000</link><description>迈季代勒沙姆斯的致命袭击并不是全面战争合理性的转折点，但它迫使双方做出回应，即使没有战略利益。真主党的反应还取决于黎巴嫩的内部事态发展，黎巴嫩自身的利益和伊朗的利益都在黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:15:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/the-response-equation-between-israel-and-hezbollah-is-stretched-to-its-limits/00000191-0859-dc27-abdb-fe79d0bb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在德黑兰被杀，情况尚不清楚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran-circumstances-unclear/00000191-0829-d117-abd9-8d6f43c50000</link><description>这位长期担任政治局领导人、前巴勒斯坦总理于周三凌晨 2 点左右在伊朗首都被暗杀。中东新闻网站称他被从伊朗境外发射的精确制导导弹杀死</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-31/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-political-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran-circumstances-unclear/00000191-0829-d117-abd9-8d6f43c50000</guid></item></channel></rss>